{"tid":2079912,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［突發］譚惠珠：《國安法》可能係星期日（周未）就會通過！","createTime":"2020-06-26T05:57:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-26T07:12:57.000Z","uid":219007,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"b226db6b83e97d8babd234efac9c5e14df119fbd","tid":2079912,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T05:57:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20200626/s00001/1593139470882/港區國安法-譚惠珠料周末有機會投票-稱條文待草案敲定才公布\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20200626%2Fs00001%2F1593139470882%2F%E6%B8%AF%E5%8D%80%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95-%E8%AD%9A%E6%83%A0%E7%8F%A0%E6%96%99%E5%91%A8%E6%9C%AB%E6%9C%89%E6%A9%9F%E6%9C%83%E6%8A%95%E7%A5%A8-%E7%A8%B1%E6%A2%9D%E6%96%87%E5%BE%85%E8%8D%89%E6%A1%88%E6%95%B2%E5%AE%9A%E6%89%8D%E5%85%AC%E5%B8%83&d=b6PV2mHT5tDC6%2Fq4CXK2Sgx1bwA8BEbsE0NvOM0S0Pc%3D&h=bd09ba52\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20200626%2Fs00001%2F1593139470882%2F%E6%B8%AF%E5%8D%80%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95-%E8%AD%9A%E6%83%A0%E7%8F%A0%E6%96%99%E5%91%A8%E6%9C%AB%E6%9C%89%E6%A9%9F%E6%9C%83%E6%8A%95%E7%A5%A8-%E7%A8%B1%E6%A2%9D%E6%96%87%E5%BE%85%E8%8D%89%E6%A1%88%E6%95%B2%E5%AE%9A%E6%89%8D%E5%85%AC%E5%B8%83&h=b0559fe1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20200626/s00001/1593139470882/港區國安法-譚惠珠料周末有機會投票-稱條文待草案敲定才公布</a><br />\n<br />\n全國人大常委會本月28至30日（下周日至周二）開會，料繼續審議「港區國安法」。基本法委員會副主任譚惠珠今早（26日）於港台節目表示， 港區國安法立法事在必行，「很有可能性在這次通過&hellip;&hellip;<span style=\"color: red;\">有機會在這個周末投票</span>」。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大陸嘅週末係包埋星期日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n28/6 星期日就係開會嘅第一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n譚惠珠稱，以她所知經人大常委投票後，港府需要刊憲後港區國安法才生效，但「可以synchronize（同步），令投票時間及刊憲時間好近」。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">因為如果目標真係要喺7月1號之前通過同執行，30號先表決其實好倉猝。照常理佢應該會愈多一兩日。 所以星期日會通過真係唔出奇</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1948d105f33610389480c259fc50c0d5472d8936","tid":2079912,"uid":188176,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T05:59:01.000Z","msg":"佢呢d權力邊緣人知西咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連份稿都未睇過"},{"pid":"568173a626dbc70f8748be2915d03f9761688a86","tid":2079912,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T05:59:31.000Z","msg":"今日有活動<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">攬炒團隊</span></span>聯繫到喺EU有一定影響力嘅Martens Centre think tank 討論歐盟可以點支援香港！<br />\n<br />\n嘉賓：<br />\n#斯洛伐克前總理 Mikul&aacute;&scaron; Dzurinda、#歐洲議會議員 Miriam Lexmann MEP、#梁繼平 手足<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">時間：<br />\n26/6 (五) 香港時間1645-1745</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n詳情：<br />\n<a href=\"https://facebook.com/events/s/hong-kong-under-the-dragons-br/713316162815311\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffacebook.com%2Fevents%2Fs%2Fhong-kong-under-the-dragons-br%2F713316162815311&d=b6PV2mHT5tDC6%2Fq4CXK2Sgx1bwA8BEbsE0NvOM0S0Pc%3D&h=734bcb70\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://facebook.com/events/s/hong-kong-under-the-dragons-br/713316162815311</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TbVyMMe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTbVyMMe.jpg&h=8f0dca4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">【626攬炒團隊 歐盟戰線新嘗試！】</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2079331\" dat